{"name":"Flame Breath","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Using his body as a conduit for his Warp-drawn power, the psyker expels a torrent of flame from his mouth and eyes. Even his allies can find the sight terrifying as his foes are burned with his unnatural exhalations.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Attack target at range with cone of flame","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 3","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"20*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack","effect":"","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"1d10+2+2*PR","penetration":"0","special":"Flame"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"0w1E3Zn8EJE3RRYQ"}
{"name":"Inferno","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Focussing his power, the psyker ignites the very atmosphere surrounding his target, placing his foe in the midst of a sudden and violent conflagration.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Attack the target at range with an explosion  of fire","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 5","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack, Concentration","effect":"","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"2d10+3*PR","penetration":"0","special":"Blast (PR), Flame"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"5zeYEmm7KxztTjPQ"}
{"name":"Fiery Form","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Unnatural flame engulfs the psyker&rsquo;s entire body. He is cloaked in sheets of fire that somehow do not harm him, but burns any nearby with horrifying results.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Summon a burning wall of fire","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 4","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"Self","sustained":"Half Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>While this power is in effect, all of the psyker&rsquo;s melee attacks deal additional Energy damage equal to his psy rating and gain the Flame quality. In addition, at the end of each of the psyker&rsquo;s turns in which he sustains this power, he emits a Psychic Blast centred on his location. Each character within the area of the blast, with the exception of the psyker himself, are struck.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"1d10+PR","penetration":"0","special":"Blast (PR), Flame"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"JYD4z12WhU6RWqId"}
{"name":"Manipulate Flame","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Reaching out with his mind, the psyker grasps nearby flame and moulds it to his desire. The flames dance to his tune, moving to untouched areas or falling quiet at their master&rsquo;s command.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Extinguish or control fire","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 35","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":20,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"Half Action","subtype":"Attack","effect":"<p>The psyker chooses a patch of fire in range and line of sight with a radius no greater than PR metres. Each round, he can either extinguish or control the fire. If he extinguishes the fire, this power ends and the fire goes out. If he controls the fire, he can move it up to a number of metres equal to his psy rating per round along a flammable surface.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"LtZJa5057mjjYC8u"}
{"name":"Fire Shield","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>With but a gesture, the psyker summons a wall of shimmering, unnatural fire in the air before him. Any who would strike the pyromancer must contend with fiery retribution, as flames leap outward, travelling in reverse down the path of the bullet or lasbolt to strike the psyker&rsquo;s assailant.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Surround body in spectral flame","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Agiility 40","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"20*PR","sustained":"Free Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>While this power is in effect, any character in range and line of sight that successfully strikes the psyker with an attack immediately suffers Energy damage equal to the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating. The degrees of success on this attack are equal to those from the Focus Power test, and the inflicted damage is not reduced by Armour or Toughness bonus.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"PR","penetration":"0","special":"Flame"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"MKU7TtYWc576OE5a"}
{"name":"Molten Beam","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The pyrokine projects from his hands a blindingly bright beam of sun-hot energy. At the touch of this blazing ray, plasteel liquefies and flesh bursts into ash.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Attack target at range with a beam of energy","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 4","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"5*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack","effect":"","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"1d10+5+3*PR","penetration":"2*PR","special":"Melta"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"ScX159vOHi6L8CC2"}
{"name":"Spontaneous Combustion","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>In one of the purest displays of his power, the psyker ignites his enemies, burning them alive. The target&rsquo;s blood boils and flesh smoulders, and as the psyker&rsquo;s rage reaches its pinnacle, the target&rsquo;s body begins to explode in blasts of ash and flame.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Cause target to  catch fire","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 40","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"20*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack","effect":"","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"1d10+2+2*PR","penetration":"0","special":"Flame"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Z1hwGw0M4AVzYq1d"}
{"name":"Sunburst","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The psyker releases a nova of fiery energy from his body. As the psyker focuses his power, a blazing aura coalesces around him, growing brighter and hotter before rapidly expanding outward in all directions. As the calm at the eye of the firestorm, the psyker is untouched, while all around him is reduced to ash and cinder.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Release a nova of fire","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 4","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"20*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack","effect":"","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"1d10+2+2*PR","penetration":"0","special":"Flame"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"cIZsZFZnkEMfy5Rf"}
{"name":"Cauterise","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>With careful application of his powers, the psyker applies intense heat to a wound on his own flesh or to the flesh of an ally, quenching the flow of blood. The effect is quite painful, but certainly preferable to bleeding to death. The use of this power generates a focused and intense heat that rivals advanced medicae equipment, and certainly far exceeds the effects of ordinary battlefield cauterisations.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Remove blood loss from target","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 45","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":20,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"1","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker chooses himself or another character he can physically touch. If the target is suffering from Blood Loss, successfully using the power removes that condition.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/ifrit.svg","effects":[],"_id":"gC04yhHShAEoDkUW"}
